  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST NOW!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/702f744d251d916a158d046e0e69e44d.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/702f744d251d916a158d046e0e69e44d.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/702f744d251d916a158d046e0e69e44d.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oh Baby! It's time for racing! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>OH BABY! KART</strong>, racing like you have never seen before! Innovative drift boost and ultimate abilities! Select your driver, customize your kart and get ready to race!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drifting Ultimate Abilities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/d5b013c371693af41e63528c3398379c.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=616 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/d5b013c371693af41e63528c3398379c.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/d5b013c371693af41e63528c3398379c.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Drifting gives you powers, ULTIMATE powers! Speed boost? Rockets? Freezing bams and booms? Pick your style and play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect them all? Collect them all!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/f37d57c39a460830e62432570b8a28ee.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/f37d57c39a460830e62432570b8a28ee.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/f37d57c39a460830e62432570b8a28ee.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Whales, Butters and fast cars! There's karts for everyone! Decorate them with ornaments to show off your achievements or plain \"whaat?\", we got chopsticks, umbrellas or even pets for those long rides! The possibilities are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTENSE MULTIPLAYER ACTION</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/6f87e0dbd97808ff5b3b686d63ab95b4.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/6f87e0dbd97808ff5b3b686d63ab95b4.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/6f87e0dbd97808ff5b3b686d63ab95b4.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Go against competitors all over the world! Party up or go solo and get that position on the global leaderboards! More into fun play? Setup a custom lobby with your friends! You can show your mastery of the tracks or how you use your ultimates everywhere! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHALLENGE MODE</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/5cf362cc763c559b7c83d05ebc696a3c.avif?t=1760426386\" width=609 height=153 /></span>We got more! Go on the adventure maps! A fusion of skill-based trials, daring obstacle courses and unique competitive scenarios you can put your skills to the test!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/04f42029a19372491cfad4db2ba26bf2.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/04f42029a19372491cfad4db2ba26bf2.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/04f42029a19372491cfad4db2ba26bf2.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oh Baby!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oh Baby! It's time for racing! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>OH BABY! KART</strong>, racing like you have never seen before! Innovative drift boost and ultimate abilities! Select your driver, customize your kart and get ready to race!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drifting Ultimate Abilities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/d5b013c371693af41e63528c3398379c.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=616 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/d5b013c371693af41e63528c3398379c.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/d5b013c371693af41e63528c3398379c.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Drifting gives you powers, ULTIMATE powers! Speed boost? Rockets? Freezing bams and booms? Pick your style and play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect them all? Collect them all!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/f37d57c39a460830e62432570b8a28ee.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/f37d57c39a460830e62432570b8a28ee.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/f37d57c39a460830e62432570b8a28ee.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Whales, Butters and fast cars! There's karts for everyone! Decorate them with ornaments to show off your achievements or plain \"whaat?\", we got chopsticks, umbrellas or even pets for those long rides! The possibilities are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTENSE MULTIPLAYER ACTION</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/6f87e0dbd97808ff5b3b686d63ab95b4.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/6f87e0dbd97808ff5b3b686d63ab95b4.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/6f87e0dbd97808ff5b3b686d63ab95b4.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Go against competitors all over the world! Party up or go solo and get that position on the global leaderboards! More into fun play? Setup a custom lobby with your friends! You can show your mastery of the tracks or how you use your ultimates everywhere! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHALLENGE MODE</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/5cf362cc763c559b7c83d05ebc696a3c.avif?t=1760426386\" width=609 height=153 /></span>We got more! Go on the adventure maps! A fusion of skill-based trials, daring obstacle courses and unique competitive scenarios you can put your skills to the test!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/04f42029a19372491cfad4db2ba26bf2.poster.avif?t=1760426386\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/04f42029a19372491cfad4db2ba26bf2.webm?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598980/extras/04f42029a19372491cfad4db2ba26bf2.mp4?t=1760426386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oh Baby!</strong></p>",
